        "text_wh3cnU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The FrostClip isn’t your typical cheap plastic fan.<br/>It wasn’t designed to just sit on a desk.<br/>It wasn’t made with a weak battery that dies by noon.</p><p>It was engineered for <strong>extreme environments and rugged outdoor use</strong> — helping people who literally cannot escape the heat.</p><p>Users quickly noticed something unexpected: — They weren’t just surviving the heat — their <strong>overall energy levels dramatically improved.</strong></p><ul><li>No more sticky, sweaty shirts<br/></li><li>Freedom to use both hands while working<br/></li><li>Built-in LED flashlight for night emergencies<br/></li><li>Unbreakable silicone drop-proof case — <em>it survives the toughest conditions</em><br/></li></ul><p>It didn’t take long for <strong>commuters and travelers</strong> to realize:</p><p>If the FrostClip can keep outdoor workers cool…<br/><br/><strong>could it make summer commutes bearable, too?</strong></p><p>Spoiler: <strong>Yes.</strong> And now — it’s available for everyone.</p>",
            "text_size": 16,
            "text_color": "#000000",
            "highlighted_text_color": "#000000",
